I built this map in my free time because i want to kill an enemy and see how his body falls 53 floors from a skyscraper! XD

This is a bomb/defuse map, CTs must defuse the bomb before it destroy de building!

Terrorist and Counter-terrorists must have careful whit the ventilation! there is always a camp rat in there... ;)

and remember!  don't fall through the windows!!!
